name.k: Sky 星を紡ぐ子どもたち

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 懷著溫暖的心一同冒險吧
思いやりに溢れた世界で仲間と楽しもう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 翱翔天空王國，在雲上追夢
仲間と一緒に空の世界を冒険
化身光之子 返還墜落星辰

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: From the mind of gaming visionary Jenova Chen, Sky: Children of the Light is full of enchanting delights. Soar over rolling hills, through voluminous cloud formations, and across stunning vistas as you explore a remarkable fantasy world. Every puzzle unlocks unexpected paths; clever social features make flying together as easy as holding hands. So go on. Take a leap.
